N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 92.3 - Valuation of other items

State Regulations

The superintendent may determine the amount of the liability for other items involving actuarial calculations, such as supplementary contracts not involving life contingencies, unreported claims, and dividends payable during the next calendar year. Notes
